            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">Αὐτοκράτωρ Καῖσαρ θεοῦ Τραιαν</supplied>οῦ Παρθικοῦ υἱός θεο<supplied reason="lost">ῦ Νέρουα</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">υἱωνός Τραιανὸς Ἁδριανὸς Σεβ</supplied>αστός ἀρχιερεὺς μέγισ<supplied reason="lost">τος</supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">δημαρχικῆς ἐξουσίας τὸ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ὕ</supplied>πατος τὸ γ' πατὴ<supplied reason="lost">ρ πα</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">τρίδος Προυσαέων πρὸς τῷ Ὀλύμ</supplied>πῳ τοῖς ἄρχουσι καὶ τ<supplied reason="lost">ῇ βου</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">λῇ καὶ τῷ δήμῳ χαίρειν. ἡ υπ' ἐ</supplied>μοῦ πεμφθεῖσα ὑμῖν δ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ραν καὶ τὰ θερμὰ ὕδατα <supplied reason="lost">ἐκ</supplied> <lb n="7"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἀμφισβήτησις. ε<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> in qua Terentii Eros et Meno<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div></div>
